4. `length()` - Return total number of items
5. `map(fn)` - Apply function to all items
6. `foldl(fn, initial)` - Fold/reduce from the left
7. `foldr(fn, initial)` - Fold/reduce from the right
8. `reverse()` - Return list with items in reversed order

Constraints:
- No Array.prototype functions (no push, map, filter, reduce, reverse, etc.)
